doc.name: document
doc.content:
<svg style="height:0">
  <defs>
    <filter id="cat-bubble" x="-0.2" y="-0.2" width="1.4" height="1.4" filterUnits="objectBoundingBox">
      <feMorphology operator="dilate" in="SourceGraphic" radius="0" result="dilate"/>
      <feGaussianBlur result="blur" in="dilate" stdDeviation="3"/>
      <feMerge>
        <feMergeNode in="blur"/>
        <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
      </feMerge>
    </filter>
  </defs>
</svg>
